      "en": "Like quote(), but also replace spaces with plus signs, as required for quoting HTML form values when building up a query string to go into a URL. Plus signs in the original string are escaped unless they are included in safe. It also does not have safe default to '/'. Example: quote_plus('/El Niño/') yields '%2FEl+Ni%C3%B1o%2F'."
